                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d967">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Sultan of Turkey</gloss> to President
                            <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Yildiz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-03-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 25, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Very much touched by the felicitations you have been so good as to express to me
                    on the occasion of the Bairam. I return especial thanks.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Abdul Hamid.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
